%define distro tablet
Name: installer-distro-%distro
Version: 6.0
Release: alt3

Summary: Installer files for Tablet distros 
License: GPL
Group: System/Configuration/Other
BuildArch: noarch

Source: %name-%version.tar

%description
Installer files for Tablet distros.

